              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "样例解释 1：吃掉第一个寿司所需操作次数的期望为 $1$。之后，吃掉第二个寿司所需操作次数的期望为 $1.5$。再之后，吃掉第三个寿司所需操作次数的期望为 $3$。因此，总的操作次数期望为 $1 + 1.5 + 3 = 5.5$。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "状态转移路线",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "想象你现在站在状态 <code>(i, j, k)</code> （有 <code>i</code> 个 1 寿司，<code>j</code> 个 2 寿司，<code>k</code> 个 3 寿司）。你吃了一口，你<strong>会走到哪去</strong>？",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>吃到 1 个寿司的盘子（概率</strong> $i/N$<strong>）</strong>：盘子空了。1 寿司盘少 1 个。你去到了状态 <code>dp[i-1][j][k]</code>。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>吃到 2 个寿司的盘子（概率</strong> $j/N$<strong>）</strong>：盘子剩 1 个寿司。2 寿司盘少 1 个，<strong>1 寿司盘多 1 个</strong>。你去到了状态 <code>dp[i+1][j-1][k]</code>。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>吃到 3 个寿司的盘子（概率</strong> $k/N$<strong>）</strong>：盘子剩 2 个寿司。3 寿司盘少 1 个，<strong>2 寿司盘多 1 个</strong>。你去到了状态 <code>dp[i][j+1][k-1]</code>。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>吃到空盘子（概率</strong> $(N-i-j-k)/N$<strong>）</strong>：什么也没发生。你还在原地 <code>dp[i][j][k]</code>。",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "状态转移公式（把步数加进去）",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "既然吃一次算 1 步，那么状态的转移等式就是：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$dp[i][j][k] = 1 + \\frac{i}{N} dp[i-1][j][k] + \\frac{j}{N} dp[i+1][j-1][k] + \\frac{k}{N} dp[i][j+1][k-1] + \\frac{N - i - j - k}{N} dp[i][j][k]$$\n右边出现了 `dp[i][j][k]`，把它移项到左边去：\n$$dp[i][j][k] - \\frac{N - i - j - k}{N} dp[i][j][k] = 1 + \\dots(右边剩下那三项)$$",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "化简等号左边：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$\\frac{i + j + k}{N} dp[i][j][k] = 1 + \\frac{i}{N} dp[\\dots] + \\frac{j}{N} dp[\\dots] + \\frac{k}{N} dp[\\dots]$$\n两边同时乘上 $\\frac{N}{i + j + k}$，**完美的转移方程诞生了：**\n$$dp[i][j][k] = \\frac{N}{i+j+k} + \\frac{i}{i+j+k} dp[i-1][j][k] + \\frac{j}{i+j+k} dp[i+1][j-1][k] + \\frac{k}{i+j+k} dp[i][j+1][k-1]$$",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "枚举方向",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "既然 <code>dp[i][j][k]</code> 依赖的都是<strong>寿司总数比它少</strong>的状态（比如 <code>j-1</code> 虽然导致 <code>i+1</code>，但总数还是少了一个），我们只需要写三个 for 循环，从小到大遍历即可。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "每次先把总数少的先处理掉，故枚举 $k \\to 0, j \\to 0, i \\to 0$。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tvar cnt = vector<int>(4);\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tint x; cin >> x;\n\t\tcnt[x]++;\n\t}\n\tvar dp = Vec3<db>(n + 1, n + 1, n + 1);\n\tfa(k, 0, n)fa(j, 0, n)fa(i, 0, n) {\n\t\tif (k == 0 and j == 0 and i == 0)continue;\n\t\tint sum = i + j + k;\n\t\tif (sum > n)continue;\n\t\tdp[i][j][k] = n * 1.0 / sum;\n\t\tif (i)dp[i][j][k] += i * 1.0 / sum * dp[i - 1][j][k];\n\t\tif (j)dp[i][j][k] += j * 1.0 / sum * dp[i + 1][j - 1][k];\n\t\tif (k)dp[i][j][k] += k * 1.0 / sum * dp[i][j + 1][k - 1];\n\t}\n\tcout << fixed << setprecision(12) << dp[cnt[1]][cnt[2]][cnt[3]] << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
